~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : chear                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : chear <roomname> all/swears/nothing

   This sets what part of the conversation in the clones room the clone 
   will display to you.  "all" makes it show all that is being said and 
   emoted, "swears" will make it just report swearing (based on the 
   swear_words array in podnuts.h) and nothing will force it to ignore 
   everything.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : clone, destroy, allclones, myclones, csay, switch
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+ 
